Enshadowed reserved FG at 9:00am PST.<br>
Roatus started killing FG at 5:00am PST as he did everyday to check Ragefire.<br>
Roatus haven't been checking reservation board because he is too lazy to do it<br>
and FGs are not often reserved in this time zone.<br>
Roatus stopped killing FGs at throne room and put druid alt for tracking<br>
and went to kael to camp some armor pieces. <br>
Roatus got Ragefire on track around 8:00am PST and gathered up people,<br>
restarted killing rest of FGs on the way to lair.<br>
Enshadowed noticed that we were there and came up and warned when we killed lair FGs.<br>
Roatus checked board and noticed that he ignored &quot;reservation&quot;.<br>
Roatus apologized about that and talked about solution.<br>
Enshadowed was planning to gather up ppl &quot;later&quot; but Roatus killed FGs too early.<br>
Enshadowed was kind enough to share the chance of Ragefire for us.<br>
Both clerics rolled for Ragefire, my guildmate lost and Enshadowed(Steelangus) won.<br>
There was about 1 Enshadowed group and 3 Soul of Samurai groups,<br>
We killed Ragefire and Steelangus got heart.(Congrats)<br>
<br>
FAQ:<br>
Q1.FG is 6 hours spawn, shouldn't long time spawn like this be reservable?<br>
A1.Stupid Verant makes average 1 servers down in 1 week.<br>
To make Ragefire, Naggy must be dead and need to make 24 - 72 hours interval after that.<br>
Even if there is no &quot;emergency&quot; server down and it goes smooth,<br>
there are only 1 or 2 chance of Ragefire in week.<br>
On the other hand, FG has &quot;static&quot; respawn time, if you keep killing them<br>
you can do 28 times in a week.<br>
FG just gives you middle-high range item.<br>
Ragefire gives cleric epics which is &quot;necessary&quot; to &quot;enjoy&quot; this game.<br>
No one wants to sit in front of screen for 3 hours just to wait to res 40 ppl.<br>
And you can't evade massive deaths at high level raid.<br>
FG should be FCFS for Ragefire.<br>
You can easily imagine which has higher priority.<br>
<br>
Q2.Why can't you talk with ppl who reserved FG?<br>
A2.There are two ways to contact with ppl who reserved FG.<br>
One is, to reply to the post. But this will cause board camp,<br>
many cleric will be mad to get sheet on each FG raids.<br>
And there is no promise of response from Raid leader.<br>
Another way is, to send tell directly in game.<br>
But this works only when the raid leader is online at same time.<br>
For example, we start playing EQ at 8pm in our country.<br>
FG is reserved at 2am and leader won't come online until that time.<br>
Do we need to wait until 2am ?<br>
Hell no, 2am is the time to stop playing EQ and go to bed.<br>
Not everyone is playing EQ like 12 hours per a day.<br>
<br>
Q3.Then why don't you contact those ppl much earlier? Like 3 days before you go FG.<br>
A3.FG is doable with 2 ppl. Do i need to ask around to kill orc pawn in EC?<br>
And this can cause another board camp.<br>
&quot;Sorry you are the 13th person who asked Ragefire after our FG raid.&quot;<br>
<br>
Q4.If you complain like this, why don't you reserve your own FG(Ragefire)? It's not hard.<br>
A4.Another possibility of VS nightmare. It would be worse because Ragefire is random.<br>
I will get along with this reservation rule for a while<br>
but this must be changed soon.<br>
<br>
Q5.FG area is good place to practice raid skills.<br>
A5.Go somewhere else. As everyone said, ice giant is same.<br>
No reason to insist on FireGiants.<br>
<br>
Q6.When young ppl go and look FG it is impressive.<br>
A6.Everywhere is impressive at first visit. Not only FG.<br>
<br>
Q7.But FG is long time spawn, we don't need to be bothered by respawn.<br>
A7.There is no &quot;safety&quot; in any raid. <br>
Look at post 50 raid places.<br>
Chardok:Around 20 min fast respawn.<br>
Sebilis:16 - 180 min mixed respawn.<br>
Like this, there is no places safe like FG.<br>
If you realy want to &quot;practice&quot;<br>
go and kill Ice Giants which is harder, and you will get more skill<br>
and will learn how to kill mobs efficiently in time.<br>
<br>
Q8.I want tranix crown/mithril armors!<br>
A8.Just pay for it or wait until you get &quot;enough&quot; level to kill those giants.<br>
<br>
Q9.But Mithril torque and mask are no drop!<br>
A9.If you still need those, you can get EXP in SolB.<br>
Stay in dungeon and wait till someone come and kill FG.<br>
It is not hard to ask them to loot those items since those are common drop and often get destroyed.<br>
<br>
What i want to say:<br>
Simply... FG SHOULDN&quot;T BE RESERVABLE ANY MORE.<br>
Another rand here.<br>
FG &quot;was&quot; needed to be reservable, but it &quot;is&quot; not now.<br>
This game is dynamic, we must see how this game is going &quot;now&quot;<br>
I wish to have another vote on FG again.<br>
<br>
